<div id="main" class="container-fluid show-body" >
  <div class="row my-card justify-content-center mx-2 mt-5">
    <div class="col-lg-5 show-photo">
      <%= attachment_image_tag @facility, :image, size:"550x550", fallback: "no-image.jpeg", class:"card-img-top", format: "jpeg" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-7">
      <h1 class="sauna-name"><%= @facility.sauna_name %></h1>

      <table class="table show-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="item">郵便番号</td>
          <td><%= @facility.postal_code %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">都道府県</td>
          <td><%= @facility.prefecture %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">住所</td>
          <td><%= @facility.address %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">電話番号</td>
          <td><%= @facility.phone_number %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">サウナ室温</td>
          <td><%= @facility.temperature %>℃</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">水風呂温度</td>
          <td><%= @facility.water %>℃</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">価格</td>
          <td><%= @facility.price_description %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">営業時間</td>
          <td><%= @facility.working_hours %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">ホームページ</td>
          <td><%= @facility.hp %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">駐車場</td>
          <td>
            <% if @facility.parking == "有" %>
            有
            <% else %>
            無
            <% end %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="row mx-3">
      <h3>Finally, I've realized</h3>
 
          <p>After spending all day chasing the white walkers and all night with my aunt, I'd never make enough time building my own website.</p>

          <p>So, here we are, I've found this free HTML template by <a href="http://creativealiens.com">Creative Aliens </a>to put on my website, that's how at least someone can find me who want's to become an ally. It doesn't matter they are Lanisters or Greyjoys. Who cares?</p>

          <p>Just let 'em send the ravens...</p>
          <a href="mailto:jon@kingslanding.com?subject=Another free HTML template&body=Here's another one page html template I found that might be cool as upcoming website landing page. http://github.com/srizon/LazyStrap" class="btn btn-primary mt-2">Send a Raven</a>

          <h4 class="mt-4">or, keep your eyes on</h4>
          <ul class="social mt-1">
              <li><a href="https://twitter.com/MamunSrizon"><i class="fa fa-twitter " aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li>
              <li><a href="https://github.com/srizon"><i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li>
              <li><a href="https://dribbble.com/srizon"><i class="fa fa-dribbble" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li>
          </ul>
      
  </div>
</div>

